---
title: Classic Surf and Striploin Steak Dinner with Tarragon Cream Sauce
description: This surf-and-turf dish is simple, saucy and crispy. Pan-seared steaks, smooth mashed potatoes and garlic shrimp are topped with a creamy tarragon and Dijon mustard sauce. It's luxurious and easy.
